data.description: HURRY TO SEE THIS VALUE PRICED RANCH CHARMER! Welcome home to this great comfy family room with built in bookshelves and lots of natural light. Check out this large country kitchen perfect for whipping up holiday and every day meals! You will love it! Kitchen features ample cabinets, counter space, tile backsplash and appliances purchased in 2021. Family and guests alike will love gathering in this great dining area. The open concept of the kitchen, dining area and family room are perfect for entertaining. Built in shelving enhances the hallway between the bedrooms providing generous storage for your books as well as cherished collectibles. Relaxing nights start in this master bedroom with walk in closet. Large 2nd bedroom is currently the cutest nursery. Outside, you will find a porch as well as a shed for holding the lawn tools. Sellers have done so much to this home! Roof and gutters are 4 years old. HVAC and water heater installed 2016, foundation supports were added in 2018. Full bathroom remodel was completed in 2019. Front landscaping was also added. Hurry to see this one today and make it yours!
